        "content": "**M8Flow unified logs**\n\n- **OTLP** (Python apps): filter by `service_name` — `m8flow-backend`, `m8flow-celery-worker`, `m8flow-connector-proxy`.\n- **Promtail** (JVM/nginx/flower): filter by `compose_service` — `keycloak`, `keycloak-proxy`, `m8flow-celery-flower`.\n- Connector proxy lines include `m8flow_connector=&lt;token&gt;` for Loki search.\n- If panels are empty, open **Explore → Loki** and inspect available labels.",
